For a couple of years now, the Ginza line boarding platform is on the opposite side of the station, so I rather forgot that the boarding platform was in this building when I played the game and got very lost😅

For no particular reason, I believed the text that someone else was translating. However, I just came to realize that only the protagonist can move Goro Akechi's heart…
I realized the importance of trying to translate it myself... 🥹
Thanks again for the great post❣️❣️❣️

I'm not used to other languages, so I tend to trust Google and the like, but when an English speaker tells me that "you" is "the protagonist", I feel very happy!
I'm going to start listening to music today as if I'm the main character 🥹
